                     <interp inst="t18241028-97-person948" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was clerk to Messrs Marsh, Sibbald and Co. for twenty-five years, up to the time of their failure; there was no other 
               <persName id="t18241028-97-person949">
                  John 
                  Watson
               <interp inst="t18241028-97-person949" type="surname" value="Watson"></interp>
