                     <interp inst="t18241028-97-person949" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             in the house while I was there: (looking at the power of attorney) the name</p>
               <p>"
               <persName id="t18241028-97-person950">
                  John 
                  Watson
               <interp inst="t18241028-97-person950" type="surname" value="Watson"></interp>
