                  </persName>
             on that day any 3 per cent. Consol Annuites standing in her name - A. Yes, 5,450 l.; she is described as of Chichester.</p>
               <p>Q. Now refer to your transfer book - have you there a transfer of 5000 l. 3 per cent. Consols in June, 1815 - A. Yes; it is a transfer of 5000 l. of her stock. The name of 
               <persName id="t18241028-97-person953">
                  Henry 
                  Fauntleroy
